		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />NESticle will run in DOSbox, if you really want hear it.  It's sound emulation isn't all that bad (for it's time), most noticeably the DPCM was loud and unfiltered-sounding, and I think triangle channel was an actual triangle, not made of steps.

		

